      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so it's basically just sitting there in a neutral account? who exactly is in charge of it and how do we know they won't just, i don't know, keep it for themselves or something? it feels weird having that much money just out of my hands.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
