      "content": "okay i get the legal part, but it still feels like this huge pile of cash is just being guarded by some random person or company until the very end. it's kind of nerve wracking thinking about that amount of money just sitting in a vault or an account being watched over by someone else. is there any risk of it being mishandled?",
